longBusinessSummary: PT Bank Rakyat Indonesia (Persero) Tbk provides various banking products and services in Indonesia and internationally. The company offers savings and current accounts; foreign currency, on call, and other deposits; mortgage, working capital, investment, franchise, and cash collateral loans, as well as supply chain financing and bank guarantees; and micro, small and medium, and program loans. It also provides bill payment, deposit acceptance, online transaction, remittance, money transfer, business, financial, institutional, treasury and global, custodian, trustee, and cash management services. In addition, the company offers investment products and services; trade and finance services, including import and export, standby L/C, BRI RTE online system services, and letters of credit; cards; and wealth management, and business internet and digital banking services. Further, it provides life and general insurance, securities, and venture capital services. The company was founded in 1895 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.
